cn.crowdos.kernel

接口 Decomposable<T>

  • 类型参数:
    T - the type of element composed by the decomposer
    所有已知子接口:
    Constraint, Task
    所有已知实现类:
    AbstractTask, DateDeadline, DateInterval, DependenceConstraint, POIConstraint, SimpleEncryptSpatioConstraint, SimpleTask, SimpleTimeConstraint, SpatioLine, SpatioPoint, SpatioPolygon, SpatioRectangular, TemporalInterval, TemporalPoint

    public interface Decomposable<T>

    The Decomposable interface must be implement by any class that needs to be decomposed into smaller parts. Usually decomposable user-defied constraints (that implement interface Constraint) need to implement this interface.
